Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.32,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,With your eyes wide open,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.32,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Me o mihiraiteru
